"uri-changed"

 void uri_changed (WebView *obj, const gchar *uri, gpointer user_data)
Parameters:
objA WebView object.
uriNew URI loaded.
user_dataData to pass to the handler.

This signal is emitted when the URI loaded in the WebView changes.

"download"

 gboolean download (WebView *obj, const gchar *file_uri, gpointer user_data)
Parameters:
objA WebView object.
file_uriURI of the file to download.
user_dataData to pass to the handler.
Returns:
TRUE if the signal was handled (will stop all other handlers)

This signal is emitted when a download is requested.
